### 1.1 Business Description

MedCaribe Health Group is a privately held healthcare provider operating in southern and central Trinidad. The organization delivers outpatient clinical services, diagnostic testing, minor surgical procedures, and occupational health services to both private patients and corporate clients.

The group serves approximately 12,000 active patients annually across its locations. Revenue is generated through direct patient billing, insurance claim processing with local and regional insurers, and corporate occupational health contracts.

